cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on room layout estimation from a monocular RGB image using an end-to-end trainable encoder-decoder network. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as room layout estimation is an important task for robots to navigate and interact with indoor environments. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses a deep learning approach to solve the problem. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses an end-to-end trainable network for room layout estimation. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on generating or rendering graphics, but rather on estimating room layouts from images.
